description:
What is Babylon’s Buffet, and what foods does it serve? Does the Bible teach about unclean meat, or are all foods acceptable now? What about alcohol, caffeine, and other items? 

Many sincere Christians across the world are unknowingly eating at Babylon’s Buffet, destroying their bodies, and violating God’s laws of health. Satan is using appetite, diet, and certain foods to cloud the mind, and destroy the soul of millions. 

God loves us so much that He has revealed the best foods to eat, and the foods to avoid. He wants us to be healthy and happy - with a clear mind to serve Him well. He is our Creator, and who better than our Creator to tell us how to care for our bodies! Fortunately, our Creator has given us an owners manual – the Holy Bible.

In this video, we will refer to that owner’s manual and discover God’s nutrition plan designed to care for our bodies and give us optimal health! You will discover what the Bible says about unclean meat, alcohol, and more!
